name: Lara Augusta Dizdarevic
what_you_do: Lara Augusta provides 1-on-1 Energy Leadership™ Coaching focused on guiding clients towards fulfilling their highest potential while going through transitions in life.
who_you_serve: Lara serves clients who are interested in taking a more proactive approach to life by tapping into their inner wisdom, understanding what they value, recognizing their strengths and challenges, making healthier choices, building more self-confidence, and creating opportunities that meet what they most want out of life.
business_focus: Lara Augusta provides coaching and workshops focused on helping clients unlock their true potential and become the leaders they would follow.
